  "elapsed_s": 90.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A document means-- meant also that you're wear you work, therefore we are-- therefore I was such a big perfume producer, the second after Christian Dior.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And-- and at the end, in the last-- after the different breakthrough from Uman and from-- from [INAUDIBLE], they used to-- to make razzias very frequently and we used to hide in sewage canals.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody had some hiding place, and it was always the problem how to provide food because when you heard something, you had to run.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You couldn't have things to carry with you or you didn't even have things what to carry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] terrible, and sometimes it had repercussions also on those people who were working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one night-- we used to work a-- two groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A day group for 12 hours, and another group for 12 hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had-- first I was shuffling gravel off such a big rubber-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which turned a rubber line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Conveyor belt?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and-- and this line used to throw the gravel 200, 300 meters where they needed it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] we were-- you [INAUDIBLE] and you put gravel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After half an hour, an hour, you couldn't do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if you straightened out, you got hit by the German soldiers who were around you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These constructions were all done by German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one time, I had to remain for the second-- that means also for the night-- because some people didn't come-- show up, and they didn't catch enough people because everybody was hiding.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they had-- they need 1,000 workers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They got 800, so 200 continued to work, and I was one of those.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
